<template lang="pug">
.song-list
   h4(v-for="(song, id) in currentPlaylist")
    .videoId videoId: {{ song.videoId }}
    .name name: {{ song.name }}
    v-divider(v-if="id !== 0")
</template>
<script>
import { mapState } from 'pinia'
import { usePlaylistStore } from '../store/playlist'
import { VDivider } from 'vuetify/components'
export default {
  components: {
    VDivider
  },
  computed: {
    ...mapState(usePlaylistStore, ['currentPlaylist'])
  },
}
</script>

<style></style>
